<div class="title-area show-for-printable-area">
<h2>The Soviet invasion of Afghanistan</h2>
</div>
<div class="img-area show-for-printable-area">
<img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220405164729im_/https://www.arabnews.com/sites/default/files/styles/n_670_395/public/main-image/2020/04/19/2068031-348344363.jpg?itok=K7Uto127" alt="The Soviet invasion of Afghanistan" title="The Soviet invasion of Afghanistan"/> </div>
<div class="entry-meta hide-for-large no-print">
<div class="updated-ago">
Updated 24 April 2020 </div>
<div class="entry-author">
Rahimullah Yusufzai </div>
<div class="entry-date">
<time>April 19, 2020<span> 13:54</span></time> </div>
<div class="entry-meta-footer">
<div class="grid-x align-justify">
<div class="cell shrink">
<div class="entry-views"><span class="views-count-placeholder nid-1661431"><i class="icomoon-icon icon-views"></i><span></span></span> </div>
</div>
<div class="cell shrink">
